                       - TextEditor
                       - DPaint (completely new, redone from scratch, as
                                 the old one was no real MWB-icon)

         - New Drawer (X-Stuff)
           Contains:
                    - X-Palette
                    - ButtonStyles
                    - ButtonFunctions

         - The T.M.C.-Drawer now is an image-drawer :-)

